ide bar still 18mm forward from the stem.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18100631/Curve-Remlaw-gravel-adventure-flat-bar_forwardswept-and-backswept-MTB-bikepacking-bar_top-dimensions.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18100631/Curve-Remlaw-gravel-adventure-flat-bar_forwardswept-and-backswept-MTB-bikepacking-bar_top-dimensions.jpg\" alt=\"Curve Remlaw gravel adventure flat bar, forwardswept &amp; backswept MTB bikepacking bar,&nbsp;dimensions\" width=\"2000\" height=\"300\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18100631/Curve-Remlaw-gravel-adventure-flat-bar_forwardswept-and-backswept-MTB-bikepacking-bar_top-dimensions.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18100631/Curve-Remlaw-gravel-adventure-flat-bar_forwardswept-and-backswept-MTB-bikepacking-bar_top-dimensions-297x45.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18100631/Curve-Remlaw-gravel-adventure-flat-bar_forwardswept-and-backswept-MTB-bikepacking-bar_top-dimensions-800x120.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18100631/Curve-Remlaw-gravel-adventure-flat-bar_forwardswept-and-backswept-MTB-bikepacking-bar_top-dimensions-120x18.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18100631/Curve-Remlaw-gravel-adventure-flat-bar_forwardswept-and-backswept-MTB-bikepacking-bar_top-dimensions-768x115.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/18100631/Curve-Remlaw-gravel-adventure-flat-bar_forwardswept-and-backswept-MTB-bikepacking-bar_top-dimensions-1536x230.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amaz